\cf2 \cb3 <!-- PROBLEM -->\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <section class="problem reveal">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <p class="section-label">The Challenge</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <h2 class="section-headline">You have a strong organization. Your marketing isn't keeping up.</h2>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <div class="problem-grid">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="problem-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-number">01</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-title">No marketing voice at the table</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-body">Leadership makes decisions without senior marketing counsel. Strategy is reactive instead of planned.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="problem-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-number">02</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-title">Campaigns without strategy</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-body">Work goes out the door without clear objectives, audience alignment, or a way to measure what's working.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="problem-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-number">03</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-title">Agencies without direction</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-body">You've hired outside help that delivers deliverables but not results. No one is connecting their work to your goals.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="problem-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-number">04</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-title">Growth that has stalled</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="problem-item-body">Awareness, enrollment, donations, pipeline \'97 whatever the metric, it has plateaued and you're not sure why.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <p class="problem-close">You don't need more tactics. You need someone who can see the whole picture, align the team around it, <span>and make it happen.</span></p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 </section>\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <!-- SERVICES -->\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <section class="reveal">\cf0 \cb1 \
