\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="section-label">What I Do</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <h2 class="section-headline">Strategic partnership, not vendor relationship.</h2>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="section-body">I work as an embedded partner in your organization \'97 invested in your outcomes, not just your deliverables. Engagements are flexible and built around your needs.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
