\cf2 \cb3 <!-- WHO -->\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <section class="reveal">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <div class="who-layout">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="section-label">Who I Work With</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <h2 class="section-headline">Mission-driven or growth-driven, the work looks the same.</h2>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="section-body">I've spent my career in organizations where the stakes are real and resources aren't unlimited. That experience translates well \'97 regardless of sector.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <ul class="who-list">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <li>Nonprofits and community organizations ready for strategic marketing leadership</li>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <li>Healthcare, higher education, and public sector organizations navigating growth or change</li>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <li>Small to mid-sized businesses in Northeast Ohio seeking senior expertise without the overhead</li>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <li>Organizations going through leadership transitions, rebrands, or market expansions</li>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <li>B Corps and mission-aligned businesses that want marketing to reflect their values</li>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 </ul>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="who-right">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="who-right-headline">"I've always been drawn to roles where communication supports people and strengthens what the work is really about."</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="who-right-body">My career began in healthcare operations before moving into marketing \'97 and that foundation never left me. I understand how organizations actually work from the inside, how to communicate across departments, and how to build marketing systems that last beyond any single campaign or initiative.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="who-right-body" style="margin-top:1rem;">I'm based in Northeast Ohio and focus my practice here \'97 because I believe in the organizations doing good work in this region.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 </section>\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <!-- APPROACH -->\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <section class="approach reveal">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <p class="section-label">My Approach</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <h2 class="section-headline">How I work, and why it matters.</h2>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <div class="approach-grid">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="approach-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-title">Serve the mission, move the numbers.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-body">Strategy that isn't connected to what your organization is trying to accomplish isn't strategy \'97 it's activity. I start with your mission and work outward from there, making sure every marketing decision has a reason behind it.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="approach-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-title">Build capacity, not dependency.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-body">My goal is to leave your team stronger than I found it. I hire, coach, and mentor the people around me. I build systems that work without me in the room. The measure of good fractional leadership is what stays when the engagement ends.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="approach-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-title">Outcomes over deliverables.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-body">A campaign that launches on time and misses the goal is not a success. I hold myself accountable to results \'97 awareness, pipeline, enrollment, loyalty, advocacy \'97 not just the production of work product.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="approach-item">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-title">Integrity is non-negotiable.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="approach-body">I'll tell you what I actually think. If your strategy needs rethinking, I'll say so. If a vendor isn't performing, I'll name it. You deserve a partner who gives you an honest read, not just a comfortable one.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 </section>\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <!-- ENGAGEMENT MODELS -->\cf0 \cb1 \
\
\cf2 \cb3 <section class="reveal">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <p class="section-label">How We Work Together</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <h2 class="section-headline">Flexible engagements built around your needs.</h2>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <p class="section-body">Every organization is at a different stage and has different needs. Here are the most common ways we engage \'97 and all of them start with a conversation.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 <div class="engagement-grid">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="engagement-card">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-type">Ongoing Partnership</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-title">Fractional CMO Retainer</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-desc">Embedded strategic leadership on a part-time basis. I join your leadership team, lead marketing strategy, guide your team, and own outcomes \'97 without the cost or commitment of a full-time hire.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-fits">Best for: Organizations ready for consistent, long-term marketing leadership.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="engagement-card">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-type">Defined Scope</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-title">Project-Based Engagement</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-desc">A focused engagement with clear deliverables \'97 a brand repositioning, a go-to-market strategy, a campaign launch, a marketing audit. We define the scope, set a timeline, and get it done.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-fits">Best for: Organizations with a specific challenge or initiative to address.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 <div class="engagement-card">\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-type">Bridge Leadership</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-title">Interim CMO Support</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-desc">When your marketing leader departs, a search takes time. I step in to keep strategy moving, protect momentum, support the team, and ensure continuity through the transition.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 \'a0 <p class="engagement-fits">Best for: Organizations navigating a leadership gap or transition period.</p>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 \'a0 </div>\cf0 \cb1 \
\cf2 \cb3 </section>\cf0 \cb1 \
